  "text": "To better categorize the final 24 factors a number of consolidating dimensions have been developed. In total, five dimensions have been derived, three of which have been previously used in the distributor selection domain: organisational and financial strengths [CITATION_1] ; marketing abilities and logistics capabilities [CITATION_2] . Based on discussions with the expert group two further categorisation dimensions were added: relationship strength and technological capabilities. Finally, the 24 criteria were grouped into the five major dimensions as illustrated in Table 2 . ",
